| Remark | `itinerary_items.note` — `src/itinerary.rs` |
| Note entity | `src/note.rs` — `note add/list/show/update/delete` |
| Checklist | `src/checklist.rs` |
| Expense | `src/expense.rs` |
| Export notes | `export-schema.md` — `notes[]` |
