| `image_path` | Not in v3.6.0 |
| Expense image support | Future work |
| Evidence / Attachment table | Future work |
| OCR | Future work |
| Automatic receipt parsing | Future work |
| Generic Attachment / Photo model | Future work |
| `receipt convert` / `receipt promote` | Future work |
| During-trip budget control | Future work |
| Post-trip review auxiliary / Potential Actual display | Future work |

---

## Notes

Receipt Inbox is intentionally **metadata-only** in v3.6.0.

The released model treats Receipt as an unreviewed payment candidate waiting to be reviewed, ignored, or eventually promoted to an Expense in future work. A Receipt is **not** an Actual Expense and is **not** included in Planned vs Actual calculations.

