| category display label | presentation |
| note ordering | presentation |
| reservation redundancy | presentation |
| reservation period formatting | presentation |
| overview visibility | presentation |
| planned cost note column visibility | presentation |
| day overview entry collection | presentation |

**判定:** 境界は概ね健全。**2 箇所（category detail 行の `- `、reservation heading の `**`）で軽微な構文混入**があるのが唯一の綻び。Phase 3 で是正候補。

