            "{:<4} {:<10} {:<6} {:<16} {:<12} {:<6} {}",
            receipt.id, receipt.status, day_number, amount, date, trash, memo,
        );
    }
    println!();
    println!("合計: {} 件", receipts.len());
    Ok(())
}

